title: Avengers 001.5 (1999) (Digital) (Minutemen-InnerDemons)
description: This fun, one-off special issue is done in the classic Marvel style from the 1960's, with Roger Stern and Bruce Timm expertly mimicking Stan Lee and Jack Kirby respectively. A great read if you are a fan of the classics, and even if you are a modern Avengers reader only, you are sure to enjoy this lighthearted look at years gone by with tonge planted firmly in cheek. This copy is the digital version by Minutemen-InnerDemons; thanks to them for their hard work, please seed and enjoy! :-)
